      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
      "body" : "Java can&#39;t allocate array of size <code>Integer.MAX_VALUE - 1</code>, you&#39;ll get &quot;java.lang.OutOfMemoryError: Requested array size exceeds VM limit&quot;. The maximum number of elements in JDK 6 and above is <code>Integer.MAX_VALUE - 2</code> = 2 147 483 645."
    } ],
