      "comment_id" : 102180387,
      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
      "body" : "You&#39;re using a 32-bit JVM. Use a 64-bit JVM and the JVM limit will be close to 2^31. (You also need heap space available, which is not the default, and will be affected by your physical memory.)"
    } ],
